### Valid body — passes schema.
POST http://localhost:3004/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{ "user_id": "u1", "total": 99 }

### Invalid body — `total` negative, schema rejects with 400.
POST http://localhost:3004/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{ "user_id": "u1", "total": -1 }

### URL params + query schema, both typed in handler.
GET http://localhost:3004/api/users/u1/orders?status=shipped&limit=5

### Bad enum value — 400 from zod.
GET http://localhost:3004/api/users/u1/orders?status=garbage
